import React from 'react'
import {Link} from 'react-router-dom'

const LinkRoute = ({tabs}) => 
        
              {tabs.map(tab=>
                <Link className="nav-link"
                activeClass="active"
                to={tab.link} style={{color:"#A6D230",fontSize:"30px"}}>{tab.text}</Link>
			      )}

export default LinkRoute
